   - Identified all files with logging statements using grep
   - Added `#include "logging.h"` to each file
   - Replaced ad-hoc macro definitions with mappings to the new LOG_* macros
   - Replaced direct fprintf(stderr, ...) calls with appropriate LOG_* macro calls
   - Preserved all format strings and arguments

